trans-unit.source: Represents a single tab page in a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TabControl"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Representerar en enda sidan i en <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.TabControl"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: TabPage controls represent the tabbed pages in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> control.
trans-unit.target: TabPage kontroller representerar flikar sidor i en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl>

trans-unit.source: The order of tab pages in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl.TabPages%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection reflects the order of tabs in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> control.
trans-unit.target: Ordningen på fliksidor i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl.TabPages%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samlingen visar flikar i den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl>kontroll.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl.TabPages%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To change the order of tabs in the control, you must change their positions in the collection by removing them and inserting them at new indexes.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill ändra ordningen på flikarna i kontrollen måste du ändra deras positioner i samlingen genom att ta bort dem och lägga till dem på nya index.

trans-unit.source: TabPage controls are constrained by their container, so some of the properties inherited from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control> base class will have no effect, including <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Top%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Height%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Left%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Width%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Show%2A>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Hide%2A>.
trans-unit.target: TabPage kontroller är begränsad av deras behållare så att vissa av egenskaperna som ärvs från den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control>basklass har ingen effekt, inklusive <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Top%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Height%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Left%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Width%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Show%2A>, och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Hide%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Hide%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Show%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Width%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Left%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Height%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Top%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control>

trans-unit.source: The tabs in a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> are part of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> but not parts of the individual TabPage controls.
trans-unit.target: Flikarna i en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl>är en del av den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl>men inte delar av enskilda TabPage kontroller.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl>

trans-unit.source: Members of the TabPage class, such as the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ForeColor%2A> property, affect only the client rectangle of the tab page, but not the tabs.
trans-unit.target: Medlemmar i TabPage class, till exempel den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ForeColor%2A>egenskapen påverkar endast klienten rektangeln för sidan, men inte flikarna.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.ForeColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Additionally, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Hide%2A> method of the TabPage will not hide the tab.
trans-unit.target: Dessutom <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Hide%2A>metod för TabPage inte döljer fliken.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Hide%2A>

trans-unit.source: To hide the tab, you must remove the TabPage control from the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl.TabPages%2A?displayProperty=fullName> collection.
trans-unit.target: Om du vill dölja fliken, måste du ta bort kontrollen TabPage från den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl.TabPages%2A?displayProperty=fullName>samling.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl.TabPages%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > In [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/add/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)], the tab is considered part of the tab page for determining when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Enter> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Leave> events of the TabPage occur.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > I [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/add/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)], fliken betraktas som en del av sidan för att fastställa när den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Enter>och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Leave>av TabPage händelser.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Leave> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Enter>

trans-unit.source: In earlier versions of the .NET Framework, the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Enter> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Leave> events of the TabPage do not occur when focus enters or leaves a tab, but only when focus enters or leaves the client rectangle of the tab page.
trans-unit.target: I tidigare versioner av .NET Framework, den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Enter>och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Leave>TabPage händelser sker inte när fokus anländer till eller lämnar en flik, men när fokus anländer till eller lämnar klienten rektangeln för fliksidan.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Leave> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Enter>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Controls contained in a TabPage are not created until the tab page is shown, and any data bindings in these controls are not activated until the tab page is shown.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Kontroller som finns på en TabPage skapas inte förrän sidan visas och några databindningar i dessa kontroller aktiveras inte förrän sidan visas.

trans-unit.source: In [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/add/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)], the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.UseVisualStyleBackColor%2A> property lets you indicate whether the background of the tab page should render using the current visual style.
trans-unit.target: I [!INCLUDE[dnprdnext](~/add/includes/dnprdnext-md.md)], <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.UseVisualStyleBackColor%2A>egenskapen kan du ange om fliksidan bakgrund ska återges med det aktuella visuella formatet.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.UseVisualStyleBackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: This occurs only when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.UseVisualStyleBackColor%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.RenderWithVisualStyles%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property values are both `true` and the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl.Appearance%2A> property of the parent <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> is <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabAppearance>.
trans-unit.target: Det här inträffar bara när den <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.UseVisualStyleBackColor%2A>och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.RenderWithVisualStyles%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapsvärden är båda `true` och <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl.Appearance%2A>egenskapen för den överordnade <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl>är <xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabAppearance>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabAppearance> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabControl.Appearance%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Application.RenderWithVisualStyles%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.TabPage.UseVisualStyleBackColor%2A>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the background is painted normally.
trans-unit.target: Annars ritas bakgrunden normalt.
